metadata.name: Unravel People's GAZERS
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's GAZERS, which represents an inactive state of pGAZERS. Users can participate in a new Gazers NFT acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's GAZERS as credit. upGAZERS can be claimed into pGAZERS when the subscription successfully acquires a new Gazers NFT
